 to\npredict concentrations of all other elements in various presolar grains\ncondensed in supernova ejecta and matched against measured concentrations in\ngrains found in meteorites.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Oct 2017 02:33:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 Nov 2017 18:52:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 29 Nov 2017 20:53:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-24"}
