hat one cannot\nalways expect bang-bang type optimal controls.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Oct 2017 15:37:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 30 Mar 2018 16:00:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-02"}
