ous networks. Taken together, the findings\nreported here serve to establish that pruned networks represent a promising\nplatform for the creation of novel mechanical metamaterials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Oct 2017 21:39:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-14"}
